data.description: This split-level home offers ample space for you and your family to thrive. Upon arrival, you'll be greeted by a large, newly paved driveway, providing convenient parking for you and your guests. This home offers a beautifully updated kitchen, complete with modern appliances (2023), propane cooking, and plenty of counter space for meal preparation. Additionally, there is natural gas on the street! With three bedrooms and two full baths, there's plenty of room for the whole family to spread out and unwind. Plus, the potential to create and design the primary bedroom offers a unique opportunity to customize the space to your liking. Nestled on a nearly half-acre level property, your own private oasis awaits in the expansive backyard including a hot tub! This home is centrally located to all!
